= About k3s-selinux
ifeval::["{build-type}" != "srfa"]
:page-languages: [en, zh]
endif::[]
:revdate: 2026-02-11
:page-revdate: {revdate}
:community-path: reference-guides/rancher-security/selinux-rpm/about-k3s-selinux
:product-path:

`k3s-selinux` provides policies for K3s. It is installed automatically when the K3s installer script detects that it is running on an RPM-based distro.

The `k3s-selinux` GitHub repository is https://github.com/rancher/k3s-selinux[here].

For more information about installing K3s on SELinux-enabled hosts, see the https://docs.k3s.io/advanced#selinux-support[K3s documentation].
